Class HomeBasePanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • HomeBasePanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Refreshable

    public class HomeBasePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements Refreshable
    Instances of HomeBasePanel are components of Game objects. They contain all components related the the Home Base location in the game, and are shown when the player enters the Home Base.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
